@Kickstarter's brand-new offices are located in what used to be the Eberhard Faber Pencil Factory in Greenpoint, #Brooklyn. For a team that used to work in a Lower East Side tenement building where they had to do their dishes in a bath tub, this historic building is a huge upgrade. 
The renovated space includes plenty of reclaimed wood and industrial details. Many of the construction materials are sustainable, including the building's insulation, which also happens to be edible. 
